	a 3 on the difficulty scale \\(on a 1-5 scale\, with 1 being the easiest a
	nd 5 being the hardest. For more information please visit: https://www.stj
	ohns.ca/en/recreation-culture/trail-explorers.aspx This initiative provide
	s a wonderful opportunity to explore the beautiful trails throughout the c
	ity\, promoting health\, wellness\, and community connection. Please conta
	ct healthyprograms@stjohns.ca for further information.\n\nhttps://seatoday
