BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:JHC1fGMZyhgcjkZF3dAJE
SUMMARY:Beyond the Cart: Recycling & Reuse Event 2026
DTSTAMP:20260314T230637Z
DTSTART:20260321T160000Z
DESCRIPTION:Description    Have stuff to recycle that doesn't go in your ca
	rt? Bring it to the West Seattle Recycling & Reuse Collection event on Sat
	urday\, March 21 between 9:00 AM and 12:00 PM! We host this event every ye
	ar to collect items for recycling and reuse that can't go in your home rec
	ycle carts or dumpsters. Events are free and open to all Seattle residents
	. We heard your feedback and made big changes! This year\, you'll park you
	r car in the South Seattle College SOUTH parking lot. Volunteers will be a
	vailable on site to help anyone with mobility needs. Early and late drop-o
	ffs will not be accepted\, and trucks leave when full. Beyond the Cart Com
	munity Reuse & Recycling Event\, brought to you by the West Seattle Chambe
	r and the West Seattle Junction Association\, in collaboration with Waste 
	Management and Seattle Public Utilities. ACCEPTED ITEMS: Foam blocks & pea
	nuts Household batteries \\(no damaged batteries\\) Florescent tubes and b
	ulbs \\(no broken bulbs\, limit: 4 ft.\\) Small\, empty propane camping ca
	nisters Small electronics \\(TVs\, computers\, etc.\\) Small appliances \\
	(non-freon\\) Paper for shredding \\(limit: 4 boxes of paper\\) Clothing\,
	 accessories\, bedding\, and curtains in good condition Home goods and toy
	s ITEMS NOT ACCEPTED: Commercial loads Furniture or household goods Garbag
	e Yard waste Household recycling \\(items that go in your cart/dumpster\\)
	 Hazardous waste Automotive waste Construction waste Non-recyclable or reu
	sable items Car seats Mattresses TO VOLUNTEER FOR THIS EVENT\, PLEASE REGI
	STER USING ACCURATE CONTACT INFORMATION. IF YOU ARE ONLY DROPPING OFF ITEM
	S\, NO REGISTRATION IS NEEDED.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/de
	tails/beyond-the-cart-recycling-reuse-event-2026/18274203/2026-03-21T00\n\
	nFrom SEAtoday - Community & Civic
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/beyond-the-cart-recycling
	-reuse-event-2026/18274203/2026-03-21T00
LOCATION:South Seattle Community College\, 6000 16th Ave SW\, Seattle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-community
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Community & Civic
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
